<p><a href="https://meldmerge.org/">Meld</a> is a visual comparison and merger tool for developers. Meld helps you compare files, directories and projects controlled by version.</p>

<h1 id="installation">Installation</h1>
<p>Use your distroâ€™s repository, examples:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">emerge meld <span class="c"># Gentoo, Funtoo, ...</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>apt <span class="nb">install </span>meld <span class="c"># Debian, Ubuntu, Mint, ...</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>pacman <span class="nt">-S</span> meld <span class="c"># Arch, Manjaro, ...</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>dnf <span class="nb">install </span>meld <span class="c"># Red Hat, CentOS, Fedora, ...</span></code></pre></figure>

